    "\\end{mybox_orange}\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "080fe82e",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Control-SWAP\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "080fe82e",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Si el qúbit  de control está en  el estado $\\ket{1}$ los dos controlados se intercambian.\n",
    "\\begin{equation} \\label{Fig_multiqubit_CSWAP_gate}\n",
    "\\boxed{U_{\\rm CSWAP} =\\ket{0}\\bra{0} \\otimes I_4 + \\ket{1}\\bra{1} \\otimes U_{\\rm SWAP}} \\, .\n",
    "\\end{equation}\n",
    "Podemos verla en la Fig. \\ref{Fig_multiqubit_CSWAP_gate}.\n",
